summary: If you've been dreaming about aviation in Tamriel, it's time to take the first step!
descriptionHtml:
If you've been dreaming about aviation in Tamriel, it's time to take the first step!
[b]Warning! Includes only the tower!
Everything else will find the links.[/b]
Modification is done for myself, stationed in front of the [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/56533/?]Moonstone Castle[/url]. See map screnshoot.

Variants of aircraft:
[url=http://modgames.net/load/tes_v_skyrim/animacii/vozdushnyj_shar_s_fizikoj_havok/314-1-0-18469]Balloon (physics Havok)[/url]
[url=http://modgames.net/load/tes_v_skyrim/gejmplej/1/247-1-0-11869]Dwemer Skyship fully flyable[/url] 
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/24234/?]Airship - Dev Aveza[/url] 
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/19741/?]Dwemer Flying Machine[/url]

[b]installation:[/b]
In the data folder 2 files from the archive
[b]removal:[/b]
Remove Airport_Of_Whiterun.esp, Airport_Of_Whiterun.bsa

Credits: 
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/16525/?]Modders Resource Pack[/url]
author: Eltzyn
